00:00:12.952 --> 00:00:17.224
What are you going to make?
Vegetable Hot Dog Thali

00:00:27.852 --> 00:00:31.088
Ingredients required to make Vegetable Hot Dog Thali

00:00:31.316 --> 00:00:47.434
Potatoes, Beetroot, Carrots, Green Peas, Vegetable Masala, Hot Dog Buns, 
Black Pepper, Cabbage, Coriander, Tomato Ketchup, Onions, Oil

00:00:48.569 --> 00:00:54.077
Boil a few peeled potatoes, then add some salt and mash them

00:00:57.618 --> 00:01:03.445
Take a pan and heat 2 spoons of oil

00:01:10.007 --> 00:01:15.178
Add the mashed potatoes

00:01:22.075 --> 00:01:30.844
Take a cup of boiled green peas (with some salt)
then add them into the pan

00:01:34.316 --> 00:01:38.348
Add a cup of grated carrots

00:01:43.651 --> 00:01:47.104
Add some grated beetroot as well

00:01:59.948 --> 00:02:06.632
Add 2 spoons of vegetable masala

00:02:10.630 --> 00:02:14.333
Add some black pepper powder

00:02:18.871 --> 00:02:22.961
Turn off the stove once the vegetables are cooked

00:02:26.521 --> 00:02:29.919
Put it aside for 2 mins and let it cool

00:02:38.304 --> 00:02:43.688
Cut the hot dog buns right in the middle but leaving
one side of the bread still attached

00:02:53.740 --> 00:02:57.044
Grease your palms with some oil before
 handling the fried vegetables

00:03:03.959 --> 00:03:11.533
Press the vegetable mix like a sausage

00:03:16.197 --> 00:03:22.478
Put some lettuce in the buns
(you can use cabbage leaves too)

00:03:36.105 --> 00:03:39.680
Place a slice of cheese or two

00:03:41.612 --> 00:03:46.101
Add a little ketchup (optional)

00:03:47.427 --> 00:03:50.925
Add some onions slices (rings)

00:03:59.756 --> 00:04:04.012
Place the sausage shaped vegetable stuffing in the bun

00:04:08.521 --> 00:04:11.779
Add a small stem of coriander leaves

